  "title": "Sales Support cum Customer Service",
  "description": "<p>Details:</p><ul><li>Mon-Fri 8am-5pm</li><li>West Area</li><li>1 year contract</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Duties:</p><ul><li>Process sales orders, purchase orders (PO) and delivery orders (DO) accurately and timely</li><li>Provide administrative and sales support to the sales team</li><li>Coordinate with customers, warehouse, logistics, and operations teams to ensure smooth order fulfilment</li><li>Support operational activities when required, including scheduling, documentation, and coordination</li><li>Handle customer enquiries, order status updates, and related documentation</li><li>Maintain accurate records, invoices, and basic reports</li></ul><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>At least 1–2 years of experience in customer service, sales support, or administrative roles</li><li>Familiar with processing PO, DO, invoices, and basic order documentation</li><li>Comfortable liaising with customers, sales, logistics, and operations teams</li></ul><p></p><p></p><p>Interested Applicants, please click Apply Now</p><p><br /></p><p>Chow Zi Qing</p><p>R2199258</p><p>Revup Proservices Pte Ltd</p><p>EA.24C2366</p>",
